\c 4
\s Uluthi lwesibane lezihlahla zemihlwathi
\p
\v 1 Ingilosi eyayikhuluma lami yabuya futhi, yangivusa\x + 1.19.\x*, njengomuntu ovuswa ebuthongweni bakhe\x + Dan. 8.18; 10.9; Jona 1.5.\x*.
\v 2 Yathi kimi: Ubonani? Ngasengisithi: Ngibonile, khangela-ke uluthi lwesibane lwegolide lonke\x + Eks. 25.31.\x*, lomganu phezu kwesihloko salo\x + Tshu. 12.6.\x*, lezibane zalo eziyisikhombisa phezu kwalo\x + Eks. 25.37; Isam. 4.5; Isam. 1.12.\x*; kulezimpompi eziyisikhombisa leziyisikhombisa ezingasezibaneni, eziphezu kwesihloko salo.
\v 3 Lezihlahla zomhlwathi ezimbili eceleni kwalo, esinye ngakwesokunene\x + 4.11; Isam. 11.4.\x* komganu, lesinye ngakwesokhohlo kwawo\x + Tshu. 12.6.\x*.
\v 4 Ngasengiphendula ngikhuluma kuyo ingilosi eyayikhuluma lami, ngisithi: Lezizinto ziyini, nkosi yami\x + 1.19.\x*?
\v 5 Ingilosi eyayikhuluma lami yasiphendula yathi kimi\x + 1.19.\x*: Kawazi yini ukuthi lezizinto ziyini? Ngasengisithi: Hatshi, nkosi yami\x + 4.13.\x*.
\v 6 Yasiphendula yakhuluma lami isithi: Leli yilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* kuZerubhabheli, lisithi\x + 1 Lan. 3.19.\x*: Hatshi ngamandla, hatshi-ke ngengalo\x + Dan. 2.34; Hag. 2.21-23; Hos. 1.7.\x*, kodwa ngomoya wami, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla.
\v 7 Ungubani wena, ntaba enkulu\x + Isa. 13.2; Jer. 51.25; Mat. 21.21.\x*? Phambi kukaZerubhabheli\x + 1 Lan. 3.19.\x* \add uzakuba\add* ligceke\x + Isa. 40.4; 42.16; Hag. 2.4.\x*. Yena uzaveza ilitshe eliyinhloko\x + Hlab. 118.22; Jobe 38.6; Zek. 3.9.\x* \add ngo\add*kumemeza okukhulu\x + Ezra 3.11,13.\x*: Umusa, umusa kulo\x + Eks. 18.4.\x*!
\p
\v 8 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kimi futhi lisithi:
\v 9 Izandla zikaZerubhabheli\x + 1 Lan. 3.19.\x* zibekile isisekelo salindlu\x + Ezra 3.10.\x*; futhi izandla zakhe zizayiqeda\x + 1.16; 6.12,13.\x*. Njalo uzakwazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla ingithumile kini\x + 2.9.\x*.
\v 10 Ngoba ngubani odelele usuku lwezinto ezincinyane\x + Hag. 2.3.\x*? Ngoba bazathokoza, babone ilitshe lomthofu esandleni\x + Amos 7.7,8.\x* sikaZerubhabheli \add la\add*lawo ayisikhombisa\x + 1 Lan. 3.19.\x*; angamehlo eN\nd kosi\x + 3.9.\x*\nd*, agijima aye le lale emhlabeni wonke\x + 2 Lan. 16.9; Jer. 5.1.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Ngasengiphendula ngathi kuyo: Ziyini lezizihlahla zomhlwathi ezimbili ngakwesokunene soluthi lwesibane langakwesokhohlo kwalo\x + 4.11; Isam. 11.4.\x*?
\v 12 Ngasengiphendula ngokwesibili, ngathi kuyo: Ziyini lezizingatsha ezimbili zezihlahla zomhlwathi ezithi ngempompi ezimbili zegolide zithulule igolide liphume kizo?
\v 13 Yasikhuluma lami isithi: Kawazi yini ukuthi lezi ziyini? Ngathi: Hatshi, nkosi yami\x + 4.13.\x*.
\v 14 Yasisithi: Laba bangabagcotshiweyo ababili abema\x + Isam. 11.4; Zek.3.4; 6.5.\x* ngaseNkosini yomhlaba wonke\x + Josh. 3.11.\x*.